with version stable 0.7.24
with base    libcdio libxml2
with also    --enable-static=no --enable-shared=yes
with role    video
with trait   library makej multilib-concurrent
with source  $GNU_URL vcdimager/vcdimager-$VERSION.tar.gz
with info    home http://www.gnu.org/software/vcdimager/
with info    good 20130107
with info    last 20110318
with info    cite 'video and super video mastering suite
It is for authoring, disassembling and analyzing
both Video CDs and Super Video CDs.
It convers mpeg files to Video CD BIN/CUE-style CD images.
After writing to CDR or CDRW it can be played on any box
capable of playing VCDs.
The BIN/CUE images can be burned to CD using cdrdao or cdrtools.'
